<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THIANNAK THISEN CH139</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Zohhmanh u, sualnak a kalpitu khi, Thihnak Kalvary tlang cungah,
 Vailamtahnak thing cungah khan an tar, Keimah ca a thi kha a luang cang.

[C1]
   A kan Khamhtu a hnak chungin thisen le ti kha a chuak cang, Ka lung
   chungah um zungzal seh, Misual thiannak tiva.

[V2]
 A zaangfahnak ti thiangkha a luang cang, A kan Khamhtu thihnak hmun
 in, A zungzal in khi ka ah vaa kholh u, Thlarau Khamhtu Bawipa sinah cun.

[C2]
   A kan Khamhtu a hnak chungin thisen le ti kha a chuak cang, Ka lung
   chungah um zungzal seh, Misual thiannak tiva.

[V3]
 A thi luannak ah aa kholhmi vialte, An sual hawhra bang a thiang lai,
 Nan sualnak vialte kha hun kalpi u, &quot;Ra bai u,&quot; nan Khamhtu nih a ti.

[C3]
   A kan Khamhtu a hnak chungin thisen le ti kha a chuak cang, Ka lung
   chungah um zungzal seh, Misual thiannak tiva.

[V4]
 Ka tlau bal ti lai lo sualnak chungah, A ka Khamhtu Bawipa Jesuh, A
 thiang bikmi thlarau in ka hruai law, Na lawmhnak mui kha ka hmuhter ko.

[C4]
   A kan Khamhtu a hnak chungin thisen le ti kha a chuak cang, Ka lung
   chungah um zungzal seh, Misual thiannak tiva.</lyrics>
<key>Ab</key>
<hymn_number>139</hymn_number>
</song>